    <item>
      <title>Parameter(매개변수)와 argument(전달인자)의 차이</title>
      <link>https://junumoon.github.io/posts/20210201_parameter_and_arguments/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Feb 2021 22:33:06 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://junumoon.github.io/posts/20210201_parameter_and_arguments/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Parameter: 매개변수, 함수에 정의한 변수(variable)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Argument: 전달인자, 함수를 호출할 때 전달되는 값(value)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# 파라미터: 함수 안에서 정의되는 변수&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;plus&lt;/span&gt;(param1, param2)
	&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; param1 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; param2

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# 여기서 arg1, arg2는 변수(variable)&lt;/span&gt;
arg1 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
arg2 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# 여기서 arg1, arg2는 전달인자(argument)&lt;/span&gt;
result &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; plus(arg1, arg2)
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# result = 3&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;함수는 매개변수/전달인자를 갖지 않을 수도 또는 여러 개의 매개변수/전달인자를 가질 수도 있다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;참고:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://wayhome25.github.io/etc/2017/12/31/parameter-argument/&#34;&gt;초보몽키의 개발공부로그&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;개발자의 글쓰기, 김철수&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
